          {
            "title": "Example: Good decisions",
            "id": 126752,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Code une condition qui exécute le code si <code>replayTimes</code> est supérieur ou égal à <code>300</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" song = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Don't stop me now&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" replayTimes = \" /><text value=\"345\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" replayTimes &gt;= \" /><text value=\"300\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Your top song this week: &quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(song)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"56\" endIndex=\"74\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"song == 300\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Your top song this week: \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Don't stop me now\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>replayTimes &gt;= 300</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Correct answers",
            "id": 126753,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Code une condition pour suggérer un restaurant si le <code>diet</code> de l'utilisateur est égal à <code>vegetarian</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" diet = \" /><text value=\"&quot;vegetarian&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" veggieRestaurant = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Root&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" restaurant = \" /><text value=\"&quot;DelPosto&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" diet == \" /><text value=\"&quot;vegetarian&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Try out: &quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + veggieRestaurant)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"85\" endIndex=\"89\" /><option startIndex=\"90\" endIndex=\"92\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"!==\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Try out: Root\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>diet</code> suivi de <code>==</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
