            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Stocke la comparaison d'égalité entre <code>inboxFull</code> et <code>true</code> dans <code>showAlert</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" inboxFull = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" showAlert = inboxFull == \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" showAlert {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Your inbox is full.&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;You can't receive any more emails&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"37\" endIndex=\"54\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"inboxFull != true\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"true\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Your inbox is full.\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"You can't receive any more emails\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>inboxFull == true</code>.</p></body></html>"
